{"tid":2013726,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中國《網路安全審查法》 進口網絡產品、服務要先審查","createTime":"2020-05-12T13:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T14:20:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"854e1d412f82f7ab86184a3e4afe4ae57b1b4903","tid":2013726,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:05:25.000Z","msg":"中國互聯網信息辦公室在 4 月 27 日發出公告，指從今年 6 月 1 日起，中國將實行《網路安全審查法》，針對網路產品或服務，要中國企業在採購該些產品前，要先通過各部委聯合審查，以確保國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n文件中要求，營運者必須自行判斷採購產品可能帶來的國家安全風險，自行向網路安全審查辦公室申請安全審查。而且，營運者應透過採購文件、協議等要求產品和服務提供者配合網路安全審查。而中國媒體甚至<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直接點名：「今後蘋果（Apple）、高通（Qualcomm）、微軟（Mircosoft）等產產品出口到中國，都必須接受新的安全審核。」</span></strong>有評論估計中國當局未來對網路的監管和控制只會愈加嚴厲，甚至限制外國入口的科技產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/12/networksaftychina/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2Fnetworksaftychina%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmKWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=7fa072d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/12/networksaftychina/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"a2101a098bafb9e6338cb478199c5d18c73710ce","tid":2013726,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfdf1abccec74572202b0e3400e239b6bcebb18","tid":2013726,"uid":272119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742cc8d8823acea93486ef923fc7bd1313db5c6a","tid":2013726,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit